{"tid":1856142,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"保障醫護唔止係封關，立法限制病人行為同提高殉職金好緊要","createTime":"2020-02-01T12:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T14:55:22.000Z","uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64e3869239b7979a1bf01c7aa8b9e18416cdcbab","tid":1856142,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:53:00.000Z","msg":"1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=0b34e96e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n夠你供樓養父母老婆仔女？300萬都唔夠啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"5dc977902d4f18d934dd47b474b41abcfa111ad2","tid":1856142,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"醫護冇資源，醫管局同醫院都有大部份責任<br />\n冇足夠安全裝備係絕對唔應該番工"},{"pid":"73e8dafef5bba52162500f932c4d5c549f0ef7db","tid":1856142,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"50萬真係on9<br />\n<br />\n我係醫生 一年都月球人 你出50萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9bfe8119b82e99e0da90fc5a566d5c8ecec2da","tid":1856142,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9658bd29f342e633062a0553dc5718d7eb87cd","tid":1856142,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"加人工真係解決到問題咩？香港醫護人員已經收緊全世界數一數二高嘅人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔用啲錢請多啲人手同埋upgrade下醫療配套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫輕到醫護又benefit到市民<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係好容易造成醫療霸權"}]}